Hay Plumb https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hay_Plumb 0 Edward Hay-Plumb (1883, Norwich, Norfolk - 1960, Uxbridge, Middlesex) was an English actor and film director.He served as a lieutenant in the West Yorkshire Regiment during World War I.
